      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GODDESS OF ROCK (3) has been in great form at Hobart but also goes well this course and distance. Comes back in trip and meets both the placegetters again slightly worse at weights but has a great record with Burke in the saddle and can make it a winning hat-trick. WHIPPIN PICCADILLY (2) has strung together a host of good runs without a win. Overdue and gets chance. HAPPY CLAN (1) is another overdue for a win, the latest placing behind GODDESS OF ROCK. Deserves a win and should be in the finish again. TIDEFORD (4) split that pair finishing runner-up latest and is in the mix as well. ALPINE TROUT (6) goes very well course and distance and can measure up again.",
